---
---

<section id="servicios" class="section services">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Nuestros Servicios</h2>
      <p>Atención médica integral adaptada a tus necesidades</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="services-grid">
      <article class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none">
            <circle cx="30" cy="30" r="30" fill="rgba(59, 143, 217, 0.15)"/>
            <path d="M30 15v30M15 30h30" stroke="#3b8fd9" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Consulta General</h3>
        <p>Atención médica general para diagnóstico y tratamiento de enfermedades comunes. Obtén respuestas rápidas a tus dudas de salud.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none">
            <circle cx="30" cy="30" r="30" fill="rgba(38, 217, 163, 0.15)"/>
            <rect x="20" y="15" width="20" height="30" rx="2" stroke="#26d9a3" stroke-width="3"/>
            <line x1="25" y1="22" x2="35" y2="22" stroke="#26d9a3" stroke-width="2"/>
            <line x1="25" y1="28" x2="35" y2="28" stroke="#26d9a3" stroke-width="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Especialidades</h3>
        <p>Acceso a especialistas en cardiología, dermatología, pediatría, psicología y más. Atención especializada cuando la necesitas.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none">
            <circle cx="30" cy="30" r="30" fill="rgba(255, 184, 77, 0.15)"/>
            <rect x="18" y="18" width="24" height="24" rx="3" stroke="#ffb84d" stroke-width="3"/>
            <line x1="23" y1="27" x2="28" y2="32" stroke="#ffb84d" stroke-width="2"/>
            <line x1="28" y1="32" x2="37" y2="23" stroke="#ffb84d" stroke-width="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Recetas Médicas</h3>
        <p>Recibe recetas médicas digitales válidas directamente en tu correo. Renueva tus medicamentos sin salir de casa.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none">
            <circle cx="30" cy="30" r="30" fill="rgba(155, 81, 224, 0.15)"/>
            <circle cx="30" cy="25" r="8" stroke="#9b51e0" stroke-width="3"/>
            <path d="M18 42c0-6.627 5.373-12 12-12s12 5.373 12 12" stroke="#9b51e0" stroke-width="3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Seguimiento Continuo</h3>
        <p>Mantén un historial médico digital y seguimiento de tus tratamientos. Tu médico siempre al tanto de tu evolución.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none">
            <circle cx="30" cy="30" r="30" fill="rgba(255, 123, 123, 0.15)"/>
            <path d="M30 20v20M20 30h20" stroke="#ff7b7b" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <circle cx="30" cy="30" r="12" stroke="#ff7b7b" stroke-width="3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Urgencias</h3>
        <p>Atención prioritaria para casos urgentes. Respuesta inmediata cuando cada minuto cuenta.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">
          <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none">
            <circle cx="30" cy="30" r="30" fill="rgba(38, 217, 163, 0.15)"/>
            <rect x="20" y="20" width="20" height="20" rx="3" stroke="#26d9a3" stroke-width="3"/>
            <path d="M25 30l3 3 7-7" stroke="#26d9a3" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Planes de Bienestar</h3>
        <p>Programas personalizados de prevención y bienestar. Cuida tu salud antes de que surjan problemas.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .services {
    background-color: var(--bg-white);
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    color: var(--text-dark);
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .service-card {
    background-color: var(--bg-white);
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    transition: var(--transition);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .service-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .service-icon {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .service-card h3 {
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .service-card p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
